 TransportBook is a comprehensive transport management system for managing trucks, trips, parties (customers), suppliers, drivers, expenses, and
  billing.

  Key Features Identified:

  1. Authentication - Phone + OTP verification
  2. Trip Management - Create, track, and settle trips
  3. Party Management - Customer ledger with balance tracking
  4. Truck Management - Own trucks and Market trucks (rented)
  5. Supplier Management - Track truck suppliers
  6. Driver Management - Driver accounts with balance tracking
  7. Shop Management - Shop ledger with balance tracking
  8. Expense Tracking - Truck, trip, and office expenses
  9. Document Management - Truck documents (insurance, permits, etc.)
  10. EMI Tracking - Loan EMI management
  11. Invoice Generation - Digital invoices with PDF export
  12. Collection Reminders - Payment reminder system
  13. Reports - Revenue reports by truck and party

